Extra note

sh 2login.sh will let you login to the container os
and you will see the file we created.

$ sh 2login.sh
/ # ls
bin               lib               run               usr
dev               media             sbin              var
etc               mnt               srv
hello_python.txt  proc              sys
home              root              tmp

/ # python --version
Python 3.7.0b2

/ # exit
